---
import BlogPost from '@/layouts/BlogPost.astro';

const title = "Airbnb Cleaning Checklist Malaysia 2026 | Melaka Host Guide | 700+ Properties";
const description = "Don't lose bookings to bad reviews. The 2026 Airbnb cleaning checklist for Melaka's humid climate—zone-by-zone guide with realistic timing. From 700+ property experience.";
const image = "/images/blog/airbnb-cleaning-checklist-melaka-2026.jpg";
const date = "2026-03-18";
const category = "management";
const language = "en";

const faq = [
  {
    question: "How long should an Airbnb cleaning take in Melaka?",
    answer: "A proper Airbnb cleaning in Melaka takes 1.5-2 hours for a studio, 2.5-3 hours for a 2-bedroom, and 3.5-4 hours for a 3-bedroom condo. If your cleaner finishes faster, they're likely cutting corners. Melaka's humid, sandy environment requires extra attention to grout, floors, and dehumidification."
  },
  {
    question: "What is the most common cleaning problem for Melaka Airbnbs?",
    answer: "Bathroom mold and sand tracked in from Klebang Beach are the two biggest issues. Melaka's high humidity causes rapid mold growth on tile grout—it needs scrubbing every single turnover. Sand from beach trips gets everywhere and must be vacuumed before mopping, not after."
  },
  {
    question: "How do I remove durian smell from an Airbnb fridge?",
    answer: "Use an enzyme-based odor eliminator, not regular air freshener (which just masks the smell). Remove all contents, wipe down with baking soda solution, then place an open box of baking soda or activated charcoal inside for 24-48 hours. In extreme cases, leave the fridge unplugged and open overnight."
  },
  {
    question: "How often should Airbnb linens be deep cleaned in Malaysia?",
    answer: "Sheets should be washed after every guest. Pillow protectors and mattress covers need deep cleaning monthly. The '3-set rule' ensures you always have one set on the bed, one in the wash, and one in storage. Yellow sweat stains on pillows are unacceptable—replace protectors every 6 months."
  },
  {
    question: "Should I hire a professional Airbnb cleaning service in Melaka?",
    answer: "Yes, if you want consistent 5-star reviews. Freelance cleaners often cancel last minute, run out of supplies, or miss spots. Professional services like iHousing use industrial-grade equipment, maintain trained teams, and conduct random spot checks. For 700+ properties in Melaka, we've found reliability matters more than cost savings."
  }
];

const content = `
<div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-800 mb-2">What Must Be on Every Melaka Airbnb Cleaning Checklist?</h3>
<p class="text-blue-700"><strong>Start with the sand and end with the grout.</strong> In Melaka, 2026 cleaning standards demand attention to: 1. <strong>Floors</strong> (sand from Klebang Beach is everywhere), 2. <strong>Bathroom Grout</strong> (high humidity causes rapid mold growth), 3. <strong>High-Touch Surfaces</strong> (remotes/switches), 4. <strong>Linen Stains</strong> (sunscreen/makeup), and 5. <strong>The Fridge</strong> (leftover durian smell kills reviews).</p>
</div>

<p>Cleanliness is the single biggest factor in guest satisfaction. You can have a stunning view of the Straits of Melaka, but if a guest finds a single hair on the pillow, your rating tanks. In 2026, guests are more hygiene-conscious than ever.</p>

<p>At iHousing, we manage housekeeping for <strong>700+ properties</strong> across Melaka. Our teams don't just "clean"; they <strong>reset</strong> the property to showroom condition. Here is the checklist we use.</p>

<h2>Zone 1: The "Sand Trap" (Living Area & Entry)</h2>

<p>Melaka is a coastal city. Guests visit <strong>Klebang Beach</strong> or <strong>Pantai Puteri</strong> and track sand into your unit. Sweeping is not enough.</p>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-6">
    <li><strong>Vacuum First:</strong> Vacuum rugs, sofa crevices, and corners <em>before</em> mopping. Wet sand is impossible to remove.</li>
    <li><strong>Mop with Disinfectant:</strong> Use a fresh mop head. If the water turns grey, change it.</li>
    <li><strong>Check the Sofa Bed:</strong> Pull it out. Guests often leave crumbs (or worse) in the folds.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Zone 2: The Humidity Battle (Bathroom)</h2>

<p>Melaka is humid. Mold grows fast in shower corners.</p>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-6">
    <li><strong>Grout Scrub:</strong> Use a stiff brush and mold remover on tile grout every single turnover.</li>
    <li><strong>Glass Screens:</strong> Remove water spots/calcium buildup.</li>
    <li><strong>Hair Check:</strong> Check the drain trap and the floor behind the toilet.</li>
    <li><strong>Toilet Seal:</strong> Sanitize the flush handle and the seat hinges.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Zone 3: The Sleep Sanctuary (Bedroom)</h2>

<p>Stained sheets are an instant refund request.</p>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-6">
    <li><strong>The 3-Set Rule:</strong> Always have 3 sets of linens per bed (one on the bed, one in the wash, one in storage).</li>
    <li><strong>Pillow Protectors:</strong> Wash these frequently. Yellow sweat stains are unacceptable.</li>
    <li><strong>Under the Bed:</strong> Flash a light. Guests drop chargers, socks, and water bottles there constantly.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Realistic Cleaning Times</h2>

<p>How long should it take? If your cleaner says they finished a 3-bedroom condo in 45 minutes, they cut corners.</p>

<div class="overflow-x-auto my-8">
<table class="w-full text-left border-collapse border border-gray-200">
<thead>
<tr class="bg-gray-100">
<th class="p-4 border border-gray-200 font-bold">Property Type</th>
<th class="p-4 border border-gray-200 font-bold">Standard Clean</th>
<th class="p-4 border border-gray-200 font-bold">Deep Clean (Monthly)</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200"><strong>Studio (e.g., Silverscape)</strong></td>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200">1.5 - 2 Hours</td>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200">3 Hours</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200"><strong>2-Bedroom Condo</strong></td>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200">2.5 - 3 Hours</td>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200">4 Hours</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200"><strong>3-Bedroom Apartment</strong></td>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200">3.5 - 4 Hours</td>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200">5+ Hours</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200"><strong>Landed House</strong></td>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200">4+ Hours</td>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200">Full Day</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>

<h2>The "Smell Test"</h2>

<p>Before leaving, do a smell check. 
<br><strong>Common Culprits:</strong> Durian in the fridge, damp towels in the hamper, or stale cigarette smoke on the balcony. 
<br><strong>Solution:</strong> Use an enzyme-based odor eliminator, not just air freshener (which just masks the smell).</p>

<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

<div class="space-y-4 my-8">
  <details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
    <summary class="font-semibold cursor-pointer">How long should an Airbnb cleaning take in Melaka?</summary>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">A proper Airbnb cleaning in Melaka takes 1.5-2 hours for a studio, 2.5-3 hours for a 2-bedroom, and 3.5-4 hours for a 3-bedroom condo. If your cleaner finishes faster, they're likely cutting corners. Melaka's humid, sandy environment requires extra attention to grout, floors, and dehumidification.</p>
  </details>
  <details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
    <summary class="font-semibold cursor-pointer">What is the most common cleaning problem for Melaka Airbnbs?</summary>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">Bathroom mold and sand tracked in from Klebang Beach are the two biggest issues. Melaka's high humidity causes rapid mold growth on tile grout—it needs scrubbing every single turnover. Sand from beach trips gets everywhere and must be vacuumed before mopping, not after.</p>
  </details>
  <details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
    <summary class="font-semibold cursor-pointer">How do I remove durian smell from an Airbnb fridge?</summary>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">Use an enzyme-based odor eliminator, not regular air freshener (which just masks the smell). Remove all contents, wipe down with baking soda solution, then place an open box of baking soda or activated charcoal inside for 24-48 hours. In extreme cases, leave the fridge unplugged and open overnight.</p>
  </details>
  <details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
    <summary class="font-semibold cursor-pointer">How often should Airbnb linens be deep cleaned in Malaysia?</summary>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">Sheets should be washed after every guest. Pillow protectors and mattress covers need deep cleaning monthly. The '3-set rule' ensures you always have one set on the bed, one in the wash, and one in storage. Yellow sweat stains on pillows are unacceptable—replace protectors every 6 months.</p>
  </details>
  <details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
    <summary class="font-semibold cursor-pointer">Should I hire a professional Airbnb cleaning service in Melaka?</summary>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">Yes, if you want consistent 5-star reviews. Freelance cleaners often cancel last minute, run out of supplies, or miss spots. Professional services like iHousing use industrial-grade equipment, maintain trained teams, and conduct random spot checks. For 700+ properties in Melaka, we've found reliability matters more than cost savings.</p>
  </details>
</div>

<h2>Why iHousing's Team is Different</h2>

<p>Finding reliable freelance cleaners in Melaka is hard. They cancel last minute, run out of supplies, or miss spots.</p>

<p>iHousing employs a dedicated, trained housekeeping team. We supply industrial-grade chemicals, high-power vacuums, and we conduct <strong>random spot checks</strong> to ensure standards are met. With 8+ years managing 700+ properties, we've refined our process to deliver consistent 5-star cleanliness.</p>

<p><strong>Stop stressing about cleaning.</strong> Let professionals handle the dirty work.</p>

<a href="https://wa.me/60166996688?text=Hi%20iHousing,%20I%20need%20reliable%20cleaning%20for%20my%20Airbnb" class="inline-block bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition duration-300">
    <i class="fab fa-whatsapp mr-2"></i> Get Professional Housekeeping
</a>
`;
---

<BlogPost
  title={title}
  description={description}
  image={image}
  date={date}
  category={category}
  language={language}
  content={content}
  faq={faq}
/>
